World class faculty, research and thought leadership

Our academics work at the forefront of global business research and teaching. Business leaders, governments, professionals and the media look to us for the latest insights and theory.

 

Research at LBS

 

Research is the beating heart of London Business School. Supported by some of the world’s leading thinkers, research fuels our teaching, collaboration and conversations at the highest level. And in today’s volatile, fragile world, our contributions are more important than ever.

Learn more about research at LBS

Cost-effective strategies to build employee engagement at scale

LBS research provides effective, cost-efficient and scalable interventions to positively recalibrate the relationship between employers and employees.
